  * [Part 2 - Migration Approach & Migrating the view layer](http://howtojboss.com/2012/04/17/article-series-migrating-spring-applications-to-java-ee-6-part-2/)
  * [Part 3 - Migrating the data layer](http://howtojboss.com/2012/05/10/article-series-migrating-from-spring-to-java-ee-6-part-3/)
